text: Her swutelað on þisum gewrite þa <foreweard> þe Godwine eorl worhte betweonan Ælfstan abbod & þam hirede æt sancte Augustine & Leofwine preoste embe sancta Myldryþe <are>.
Þæt is ðæt Leofwine cænde þæt he bohte þa are æt Cnute cinincge.
& se abbod cænde þæt Cnut cing gelogode þa halig <eama> wergeld wæs into sancte Augustine <unawendedlice> þam Godes ðyowan bi to libbanne ða <hwile>.

Nu is þis se seht þe Godwine eorl worhte betweonan þæm abbod & þam hirede æt sancte Augustine & Leofwine preoste, <unnan> Leofwine preosteIIsuling landes an æt Langadune & oþer æt Gildinge &Vpund penega æt <mæssan> & healf to midlængtene on <ful>.
& æfter his dæge ga land & feoh into sancte Augustine mid & <magum> & <geborenan> mæn si abbod se ðe si.
Nu is þises to <gewitnesse>, Eadsi arcebiscop & Siword biscop & Godwine eorl þe ðone seht <worhte> & se hired æt Cristesciricean & se hired æt Sancte Augustine.
Nu sind þisse gewrite þreo, an is æt Cristes cyricean & oþer æt Sancte Augustine & þridde hæfð Leofwine preost.
